      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const rows = $input.all();\nlet previous_prompt = '';\nif (rows.length > 0) {\n  const last = rows[rows.length - 1].json;\n  previous_prompt = String(last.sora_prompt ?? '').trim();\n}\n\nconst system = 'You write ONE English prompt for an AI text-to-video model (Sora-style). Output ONLY the prompt text: no title line, no quotes, no markdown, no bullet list. The scene must work in vertical 9:16. Prefer 8-15 seconds of strong visuals. Vivid and cinematic but safe: no real celebrities or trademarks, no gore or adult content. SERIES FORMAT: This is the next episode of ONE ongoing astrocosmic science-fiction serial—deep space, megastructures, nebulae, cosmic phenomena, spacecraft or suited explorers, extreme scale, awe with light peril. Every prompt must OPEN as a direct continuation of the PREVIOUS episode final beat (same mission thread, same ship or outpost when possible—the first shot or action logically follows what viewers would have seen at the end of the last Short). Do not reset to unrelated random space scenery. If there is no previous prompt yet, treat this as the series opening. CLOSE the described moment on a transition or soft cliffhanger the next run can pick up (hatch, approaching structure, flare, jump cue). Keep loose recurring visual language (palette, craft or silhouette hints) so episodes feel like one show.';\n\nconst user = previous_prompt\n  ? ('Previous episode Sora prompt (your new prompt must OPEN as direct continuation of how this ends):\\n\\n' + previous_prompt + '\\n\\nWrite the English Sora prompt for the NEXT episode only. Same astrocosmic serial thread; vary celestial details, lighting, and camera movement without breaking continuity. Output only the prompt text.')\n  : ('The Google Sheet has no logged episode yet. Write the English Sora prompt for the FIRST episode of the astrocosmic serial: strong establishing shot, hook, vertical 9:16, 8–15 seconds of visuals. Output only the prompt text.');\n\nreturn [{ json: { previous_prompt, deepseekBody: {\n  model: 'deepseek-chat',\n  temperature: 0.9,\n  max_tokens: 500,\n  messages: [\n    { role: 'system', content: system },\n    { role: 'user', content: user }\n  ]\n}}}];"
      },
