          "name": "Google Sheets OAuth2 API"
        }
      },
      "notes": "ОБЯЗАТЕЛЬНО: отдельный лист или таблица для детского сериала. Колонка с последним промптом: kling_prompt (или video_prompt). Не смешивать с Space-листом."
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const rows = $input.all();\nlet previous_prompt = '';\nif (rows.length > 0) {\n  const last = rows[rows.length - 1].json;\n  previous_prompt = String(last.kling_prompt ?? last.video_prompt ?? '').trim();\n}\nconst nextEpisode = rows.length + 1;\n\nconst system = [\n  'You produce ONE response for the NEXT episode of a single ongoing English-only kids educational cartoon web series: counting rhymes, gentle lessons, harmless colorful preschool content.',\n  'OUTPUT FORMAT — use exactly these three labels in order. No text before TITLE:.',\n  'TITLE: one line, catchy kid-friendly episode title in English.',\n  'DESCRIPTION: one or two short friendly English sentences for a social caption (brief, warm).',\n  'VIDEO_PROMPT: one continuous English paragraph for the text-to-video model only (no extra labels inside this paragraph).',\n  '',\n  'VIDEO_PROMPT rules: Vertical 9:16. One continuous clip designed for about 15 seconds of story (the API may cap length). English only for all spoken dialogue, sung lines, and on-screen text.',\n  'Audio is mandatory: include soft upbeat child-safe background music AND clear English voiceover — warm, soft, calm, playful, preschool-teacher tone; slow, clear pacing; gentle enthusiasm.',\n  'Visuals must include a readable lower-third kids-style banner showing the exact text Episode ' + nextEpisode + ' (use this exact episode number) in a large friendly font, high contrast, not blocking the main characters.',\n  'Safe for kids: no real brands, no celebrities, no scary or adult themes, no violence. Friendly 2D or soft 3D cartoon look, bright cozy lighting.',\n  'SERIES CONTINUITY: the new scene must OPEN as a direct continuation of the previous episode final beat (same characters and setting when possible). If there is no previous prompt yet, make a gentle series premiere with a clear hook.',\n  'End on a soft beat the next episode can continue (small question, next object to count, friendly transition).'\n].join(' ');\n\nconst user = previous_prompt\n  ? ('Episode number for the on-screen banner (fixed): ' + nextEpisode + '.\\n\\nPrevious episode VIDEO_PROMPT (continue from how this ends — same show):\\n\\n' + previous_prompt + '\\n\\nWrite TITLE, DESCRIPTION, and VIDEO_PROMPT for the NEXT episode only. All user-facing words in English.')\n  : ('Episode number for the on-screen banner (fixed): ' + nextEpisode + '.\\nNo prior episode in the sheet — write TITLE, DESCRIPTION, and VIDEO_PROMPT for the FIRST (pilot) episode: establish world and recurring characters, gentle hook. All user-facing words in English.');\n\nreturn [{ json: { previous_prompt, nextEpisode, deepseekBody: {\n  model: 'deepseek-chat',\n  temperature: 0.85,\n  max_tokens: 900,\n  messages: [\n    { role: 'system', content: system },\n    { role: 'user', content: user }\n  ]\n}}}];"
      },
